node.text: With the Aviator, the heroes of the past and the high-flyers of today raise expectations higher and further than ever.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Ray-Ban on July 07, 2021. May be an image of sunglasses and text that says 'AVIATOR ON SINCE 1937'.

node.text: Created in 1937 to protect US fighter pilots against the sun’s ​sharp rays, the Aviator is the one that started it all, the original. ​
